  <title><ph audience="PMCInternal">Belmar </ph>IPC Message</title>

  <body>
    <p>The Recovery Manager sends and receives IPC messages
    from Lookup Manager, Wearlevelling Manager, Buffer Manager and Flash
    Interface;</p>

    <p><xref href="#IPC_Messages/Recovery_Manager_Received_and_Issued">
    </xref>describes the message types that are sent between these managers
    and functional units</p>

